ou!"],[1376,1651,"I will not apologize for protecting you!"],[1651,1772,"That wasn't protection."],[1805,1935,"That was savagery!"],[2060,2189,"And you didn't save me."],[2227,2360,"You terrified me."],[2585,2681,"You knew who I was"],[2681,2769,"when you married me."],[2932,3082,"When you gave me your virginity."],[3215,3386,"I knew what you used to be."],[3486,3586,"I thought I could make you"],[3586,3641,"human again,"],[3641,3707,"but you..."],[3749,3974,"You don't want to be saved, do you?"],[4012,4083,"Aria, I..."],[4379,4437,"I care about you."],[4437,4491,"God!"],[4554,4733,"You can't even say it, can you?"],[4746,4804,"Love?"],[4892,5030,"Of course, you can't love."],[5109,5280,"You really are a monster."],[5905,5955,"No!"],[6006,6189,"You don't get to fix this with a kiss!"],[6222,6297,"With sex."],[6335,6448,"Not this time!"]],"80":[[321,458,"I knew Luca was a killer."],[483,538,"I just don't ever"],[538,642,"want to see him that way."],[688,838,"Yes, I am mad at him,"],[859,1067,"but even after only a few hours,"],[1101,1242,"I also miss his touch."],[1280,1405,"You know the bed feels too empty"],[1405,1459,"without you."],[1459,1526,"You mean you don't like"],[1526,1676,"going to sleep without sex."],[2002,2189,"No, I meant what I said."],[2327,2410,"It's chamomile."],[2581,2731,"Look, I've never done this before, okay?"],[2731,2819,"What, make tea?"],[2819,2857,"No."],[2873,2961,"Well, yeah, actually,"],[2961,3324,"but I never apologized, okay?"],[3324,3503,"And I won't apologize"],[3503,3616,"for trying to protect you."],[3695,3820,"I'm sorry you had to see that."],[4575,4692,"I will say that you're right."],[4758,4859,"I lost control."],[4892,4979,"I saw red,"],[5013,5201,"and that's never"],[5201,5284,"happened to me before."],[5296,5367,"What changed?"]],"81":[[83,154,"You!"],[346,429,"You're changing me."],[600,821,"I can't think logically"],[821,980,"when I'm around you sometimes."],[980,1026,"And..."],[1205,1247,"I just want to"],[1247,1438,"kee